# ---------------------------------------------------
# Third-party / re-downloadable content (B0-T0.4, 2026-07-23)
#
# Repo is public (for secret scanning) and the LFS budget is $0, so the free
# tier's 10 GiB/month BANDWIDTH is the binding constraint - every clone redraws
# it. None of the below is authored here: it is either licensed content that
# can't be redistributed, or free content re-downloadable from its source.
#
# WHAT TO REINSTALL ON A FRESH CLONE: see Docs/AssetSources.md.
#
# Rule of thumb for anything new: if it came from Fab/a sample project, ignore
# it and add a row to AssetSources.md. If you authored or retargeted it, commit
# it - see the "authored content" note at the bottom of this section.
# ---------------------------------------------------
Content/InfimaGames/

# Fab / marketplace asset packs
Content/BulletSFX_BasicCollection/
Content/Footsteps_Volume_02/
Content/Impacts/
Content/LowPolyWeapons/
Content/Mega_Survival_Tools/
Content/VFX_Muzzle_Flashes/

# Epic sample-project source content (Lyra / ShooterGame)
Content/LyraAnims/

# Raw, unsorted animation imports. Folder2 is the dead ShooterGame import
# CLAUDE.md flags as genuinely unused - scheduled for deletion in B2-T2.4.
# The curated, load-bearing retargets live in Content/Animation/ZSAnims/ and
# ARE tracked - do not widen this to Content/Animation/.
Content/Animation/Folder2/
Content/Animation/Folder3/
Content/Animation/Folder4/

# Demo/sample maps shipped inside the packs above, plus their World Partition
# external actor data. Content/Maps/ currently holds only ImpactParticles.umap
# (from the Impacts pack) - it is NOT the game's map.
Content/Maps/
Content/__ExternalActors__/DemoMuseum/
Content/__ExternalActors__/FPS_VFX_Muzzle_Flashes_Clutch-VFX/
Content/__ExternalActors__/Untitled/
Content/__ExternalActors__/VFX_Muzzle_Flashes/
Content/__ExternalObjects__/DemoMuseum/
Content/__ExternalObjects__/FPS_VFX_Muzzle_Flashes_Clutch-VFX/
Content/__ExternalObjects__/Untitled/

# Marketplace plugins - reinstall via the editor's Fab window.
Plugins/Marketplace/

# Authored content that IS tracked, listed here so it never gets swept up by a
# broader pattern later: Content/Animation/ZSAnims/ (curated retargets),
# Content/Animation/Enemy/ (zombie anims), Content/Animation/BlendSpace/,
# Content/__ExternalActors__/ThirdPerson/ (the working level's partition data).
